    Rethink Articles:
        ✔ This little project might not go anywhere but I want see if I can take what I've learned from tags and apply that to the article pages. More specifically I want to see if I can design a method by which articles can be loaded and switched on a button press. Currently, articles are loaded using a rigid set of props being passed through components and while this might be the best solution, it makes it difficult to switch between articles wthout using redirects(which i would like to avoid). Basically, i want to make it as easy to switch between articles as it is to switch between the tag filters on the home page. Like I said, this might not work but I want to give it a go and see what happens. @done(16:35 - 06/07/21)
