                    12.10.1.15:
                        Goals / Reasoning:
                            ☐Moving the UI bar from the card page into it's own component that can then be reused.
                            ☐Will allow me to have a consistent navigation option throughout the website. Will also remove need for different nav solutions for bookmark page, tags pages and liteKnews among other areas.
                            ☐At the least, having a separate component for the large UI bar will make managing it much easier. Also possibility for further fragmentation of buttons into their own components if I wanted.
                            ☐Should function exactly the same as it currently does in the UI bar.
                            ☐Should be flexible enough to add/remove buttons where relevant.
