                    ✔ Tweaked on card bookmark controls by centering them in the area and moving the area to the right for easier use with hands. @done(12:10 - 07/07/21)
                   
                    
        

        Version 11.1 - Bug Fixes:
            ✔ Full Article link goes to blank pagRe @done(17:18 - 22/04/21)
            ✔ ScrollCheck requires a two finger up and down scroll to work...not ideal. @done(17:18 - 22/04/21)
                ✔ Solution - Increase the detection range for the scrollCheck component @done(17:18 - 22/04/21)
            ☐ If there are 2 or less articles on the page when you refresh, you might get an error.
            ✔ Changing card size and then attempting to hide articles causes an error on dev and does nothing on live. @done(18:02 - 22/04/21)
                ✔ pressing a card size empties the cleanDatabaseCall cache for some reason. My solution right now is to disable the card size controls for the time being. My intention was to rework them in the next release anyway so not a big deal. @done(18:02 - 22/04/21)

